  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the safety and performance of the Neovasc Tiara Mitral Transcatheter Heart Valve
      with the Tiara Transapical Delivery System.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The TIARA-II study is an international, multicenter, single-arm, prospective, safety and
      performance clinical study.
